---
title: Cheesy Mexican Bean Enchiladas with Charred Corn Salad
description: It’s a Mexican fiesta done properly – with beans, tortillas, lots of cheese and salsa. It’s colourful, delicious and a heap of fun. Don’t forget to dollop on the sour cream and give it all a fresh squeeze of lemon to really get the fiesta going!
